    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>The demonstrated <em>CheckedListBox </em>has <em>DataSource </em>property<em>&nbsp;</em>set to a&nbsp;<em>List </em>of <em>Customer </em>objects. <em><br />Customer</em>&nbsp;class&nbsp;defines 'ID' and 'FullName'&nbsp;along with&nbsp;other public properties. <br />The 'ID' property&nbsp;set&nbsp;to the&nbsp;<em>ValueMember </em>and 'FullName' property&nbsp;set to the <em>DisplayMember</em>.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>